Package: cprd.search
Title: Search the CPRD Aurum Medical Dictionary
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ramin", "", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ramin@example.com")
Description: A tool for searching the CPRD Aurum Medical Dictionary by keywords.
    Supports multi-keyword AND/OR searches, fuzzy matching, filtering by category,
    and exporting results to CSV. Useful for building code lists for epidemiological
    studies using CPRD data.
